  {import: "import", kind: "truck", status: "Sale", model: "F350", title: "2008 Ford F350 Super Duty Lariat Super Cab 4x4 Long Bed Diesel", price: 22900, make: "Ford", year: 2008, body_style: "Pickup", mileage: 152684, exterior_color: "Black", interior_color: "Tan Leather", engine: "6.4L Power Stroke Turbo Diesel", transmission: "5 Speed Automatic", drive_type: "4x4", vehicle_class: nil, mpg: nil, trim: nil, fuel_type: "Diesel", stereo: "AM/FM 6 DISC CD CHANGER", doors: 4, stock_number: "08F350DIESEL7616", vin_num: "1FTWX31R58EC07616", thumb: nil, description: "<div class=\"field-items\">\r\n      <div class=\"field-item\"><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>**ONE OWNER** **TURBO DIESEL** **LONG BED** **HEATED LEATHER** **TOW PACKAGE**</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>With this year's increase in output for the PowerStroke Turbodiesel V8, robust new chassis and numerous refinements to the cabin, the 2008 Ford F-350 Super Duty Lariat Super Cab 4x4 Long Bed is back in competitive form in the 1-ton pickup class.</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>The Ford F-350 Super Duty one-ton pickup has been redesigned for 2008. Under the skin, a number of major upgrades take place. Ford says the chassis is stronger than before and now has a new type of coating for improved corrosion resistance. The rear suspension has also been tweaked to improve ride and handling without compromising capability. The PowerStroke diesel engine grows from 6.0 to 6.4 liters and now makes an impressive 350 horsepower and 650 pound-feet of torque. Also new this year are higher-grade cabin materials, a standard MP3 audio jack, and available power telescoping/folding side mirrors.</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>behind that grille is a larger PowerStroke diesel engine. It's now at 6.4 liters, versus 6.0 liters last year, and features twin turbochargers a small one for quick response off the line and a larger one that kicks in to beef up the midrange and common-rail fuel injection with high-tech injectors. Because these injectors administer fuel in up to five metered spurts per combustion cycle rather than all at once, reliability is improved, emissions are reduced and the engine even runs quieter. Another benefit is quick startup this diesel can fire up in under 2 seconds at minus-20 degrees.</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>This F350 is also equipped with Factory Brake Control, Rear Power Sliding Window, Power Seats, and Power Options.</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>Give us a call to schedule a test drive or if you have additional questions.</strong></span></p></div>\r\n  </div>", other_options: "<div class=\"item-list\"><ul id=\"list-0\" class=\"veh-features-list\" style=\"float: left; display: block; width: 33%;\"><li class=\"first\">4 Door</li>\r\n<li>4x4</li>\r\n<li>Air Conditioning</li>\r\n<li>Alloy Wheels</li>\r\n<li>AM FM Radio</li>\r\n<li>Anti Lock Brakes</li>\r\n<li>Automatic Transmission</li>\r\n<li>Bed Liner</li>\r\n<li>CD Changer</li>\r\n<li class=\"last\">Cruise Control</li>\r\n</ul></div><div class=\"item-list\"><ul id=\"list-1\" class=\"veh-features-list\" style=\"float: left; display: block; width: 33%;\"><li class=\"first\">Dual Air Bags</li>\r\n<li>Extra Truck Cab</li>\r\n<li>Factory Brake Control</li>\r\n<li>Fog Lights</li>\r\n<li>Heated Seats</li>\r\n<li>Leather Interior</li>\r\n<li>Long Bed</li>\r\n<li>One Owner</li>\r\n<li>Power Locks</li>\r\n<li class=\"last\">Power Mirrors</li>\r\n</ul></div><div class=\"item-list\"><ul id=\"list-2\" class=\"veh-features-list\" style=\"float: left; display: block; width: 33%;\"><li class=\"first\">Power Seats</li>\r\n<li>Power Sliding Rear Window</li>\r\n<l