 climate control, remote engine start and hands-free Bluetooth via OnStar. Also standard are a navigation system with real-time traffic and an eight-speaker Bose surround-sound audio system with a CD/DVD/MP3 player and satellite radio.</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>Powering the Escalade EXT is a potent 6.2-liter V8 producing 403 horsepower and 417 pound-feet of torque. Power is fed through a six-speed automatic transmission with a tow/haul mode. EPA fuel economy estimates stand at 12 mpg city/19 mpg highway and 14 mpg in combined driving.</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>The 2009 Cadillac Escalade EXT comes standard with antilock disc brakes, stability control and full-length side curtain airbags with rollover protection.</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>Give us a call to schedule a test drive or if you have additional questions. Warranty available for purchase.</strong></span></p></div>\r\n  </div>", other_options: "<div class=\"item-list\"><ul id=\"list-0\" class=\"veh-features-list\" style=\"float: left; display: block; width: 33%;\"><li class=\"first\">4 Door</li>\r\n<li>Adjustable Pedals</li>\r\n<li>Air Conditioning</li>\r\n<li>Alloy Wheels</li>\r\n<li>AM FM Radio</li>\r\n<li>Anti Lock Brakes</li>\r\n<li>Automatic Transmission</li>\r\n<li>AWD</li>\r\n<li>Back Up Camera</li>\r\n<li>Bed Liner</li>\r\n<li>Bose Stereo System</li>\r\n<li class=\"last\">CD Changer</li>\r\n</ul></div><div class=\"item-list\"><ul id=\"list-1\" class=\"veh-features-list\" style=\"float: left; display: block; width: 33%;\"><li class=\"first\">Cruise Control</li>\r\n<li>Dual Air Bags</li>\r\n<li>DVD Entertainment System</li>\r\n<li>Fog Lights</li>\r\n<li>Heated Seats</li>\r\n<li>Leather Interior</li>\r\n<li>Memory Seats</li>\r\n<li>Moon Roof/Sunroof</li>\r\n<li>Navigation System</li>\r\n<li>Power Loc